XML::Stream v1.0

This module provides you with access to XML Streams.  An XML Stream
is just that.  A stream of XML over a connection between two computers.
For more information about XML Streams, and the group that created them,
please visit:

http://etherx.jabber.org/streams

Ryan Eatmon
Jabber Perl Team Leader
reatmon@ti.com




REQUIREMENTS

  - XML::Parser

INSTALLATION

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install


STATUS

  While I'm not going to guarentee that this module works 100%, we have not 
received any bug reports for a while and I've tested it for about two months.


Please send any bug reports to reatmon@ti.com.
04/17/2000
